org.springframework.boot.test.autoconfigure.data.redis

注释类型 AutoConfigureDataRedis


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Inherited
 @ImportAutoConfiguration
public @interface AutoConfigureDataRedis
    Auto-configuration imports for typical Data redis tests. Most tests should consider using @DataRedisTest rather than using this annotation directly.
